metadata.name: Who?
metadata.description:
As this sign rose above the crowd, I saw unity.. a moment where all asked one question and demanded an answer.

In June of 2020, we witnessed many around the world stand side by side to challenge unjust systems that have historically targeted and abused Black Americans. "To Protest + Serve WHO?"

More than a question, the sign captured in this image spoke to years of unfair treatment and unjust police practices.

If not us, who you are protecting and serving, who?
